<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Payment Cancelled | Arzani Marketplace</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .cancel-container {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            padding: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .cancel-icon {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            margin-top: 1rem;
            color: #6c757d;
        }

        .help-section {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            text-align: left;
            margin: 1.5rem 0;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: #041b76;
            border-color: #041b76;
            padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: #052287;
            border-color: #052287;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(4, 27, 118, 0.2);
        }

        .btn-outline-secondary {
            color: #041b76;
            border-color: #041b76;
            padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn-outline-secondary:hover {
            background-color: rgba(4, 27, 118, 0.1);
            color: #041b76;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .buttons-container {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        .plan-table {
            margin-top: 2rem;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .plan-header {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        @media (max-width: 576px) {
            .buttons-container {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-12 col-md-10 col-lg-8">
                <div class="cancel-container">
                    <svg class="cancel-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                        <path d="M12 22C17.5228 22 22 17.5228 22 12C22 6.47715 17.5228 2 12 2C6.47715 2 2 6.47715 2 12C2 17.5228 6.47715 22 12 22Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                        <path d="M13.5 8L8.5 13" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                        <path d="M8.5 8L13.5 13" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                    </svg>
                    
                    <h1 class="display-6 mb-3">Payment Cancelled</h1>
                    <p class="lead mb-4">
                        Your subscription process was cancelled. No payment has been processed, and your account remains unchanged.
                    </p>

                    <div class="help-section">
                        <h5>Need Help?</h5>
                        <p>If you experienced any issues during the payment process or have questions about our subscription plans, please contact our support team:</p>
                        <ul class="text-start">
                            <li>Email: support@arzani.co.uk</li>
                            <li>Phone: +44 (0) 123 456 7890</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <h5 class="mt-4">Available Plans</h5>
                    <div class="table-responsive">
                        <table class="table plan-table">
                            <thead class="plan-header">
                                <tr>
                                    <th>Plan</th>
                                    <th>Price</th>
                                    <th>Features</th>
                                </tr>
                            </thead>
                            <tbody>
                                <tr>
                                    <td>Gold</td>
                                    <td>£39/month</td>
                                    <td>Full database access, Advanced filtering</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td>Platinum</td>
                                    <td>£50/month</td>
                                    <td>All Gold features + Off-market leads, Priority matching</td>
                                </tr>
                            </tbody>
                        </table>
                    </div>

                    <div class="buttons-container">
                        <a href="/checkout/gold" class="btn btn-primary">Try Gold Plan</a>
                        <a href="/checkout/platinum" class="btn btn-outline-secondary">Try Platinum Plan</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
